{"tid":475544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財委會48票贊成、0票反對   通過將軍澳建海水化淡廠","createTime":"2017-11-21T08:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T02:05:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":522,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e08035ca2d495ec228af9057a3b698ad12af2114","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/bkn-20171013171117401-1013_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fbkn-20171013171117401-1013_00822_001.html&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=40485841\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/bkn-20171013171117401-1013_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">財委會通過將軍澳建海水化淡廠</span></strong><br />\n2017年10月13日<br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會今天(13日)舉行會議，審議改善濾水廠消毒設施及將軍澳海水化淡廠等項目，涉及19億億港元的撥款申請。多名議員支持興建海水化淡廠，又詢問將來可否因而減少購買東江水，議案終以48票贊成、0票反對獲得通過。"},{"pid":"23c3fec264f01bb0212224c3422009ef8b22ac41","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/photo/bkn-20171013171117401-1013_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171013195830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171013171117401-1013_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171013195830&h=35b58c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員黃碧雲支持建海水化淡廠，惟擔心早前有學者建議填平船灣淡水湖建屋，相關人士獲委任為土地供應專責小組成員，擔心批出撥款助增加水資源，但另一邊廂卻填平水塘，認為做法「戇居」，難向公眾交代。議員朱凱廸質疑，建海水化淡廠後可否降低東江水購買量。"},{"pid":"1b5dfe7b89567e1dc99996243a1c9d85646bef58","tid":475544,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"幾時先用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b986b4e03972aaec89cda3cc23f348f535526c7","tid":475544,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f03905e2d758b035766c9b13b4c836299376c2c","tid":475544,"uid":27866,"like":46,"dislike":9,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"驚西咩 之前有個連登鍵國大師話三個月夠整個供應全香港嘅淡化廠啦"},{"pid":"625fcc41d49d4527439fb7447d2b14fd7a0801af","tid":475544,"uid":12367,"like":9,"dislike":28,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"我地鍵國派又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bac6f4303a910b85ef6f468b05febd3986e2554","tid":475544,"uid":143241,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"海水淡化廠之後第二步就係發展輕工業同農業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc94b89dfc8a149d03202f9815ec5fc3ddf26a52","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海水淡化廠之後第二步就係發展輕工業同農業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高科技輕工 + 高科技農業"},{"pid":"5565baf4d80ef4feb40912b7cbd94f4d43b2fbed","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">將軍澳海水化淡廠 11億元建水管</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據水務署向立法會提交的文件，建議將將軍澳海水化淡廠第一階段設計及建造的一部分提升為甲級工程，以建設一條長約10公里、直徑1,200毫米的食水管，連接化淡廠及配水庫，造價達11.1億港元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.hket.com/article/1625163/將軍澳海水化淡廠%2011億元建水管\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1625163%2F%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%252011%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E5%BB