ree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下年東江水又加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903a2bf0c9321a102a1cd4002e37a57a3b80abb8","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下年東江水又加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加囉, 越加越起得多廠<br />\n<br />\n起多兩個"},{"pid":"07598ff369fd7002cb31530f11a615461db7184c","tid":475544,"uid":143241,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海水淡化廠之後第二步就係發展輕工業同農業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高科技輕工 + 高科技農業</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">MAKE HONG KONG GREAT AGAIN</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad265236bd88851b731ac5522c8c27af7f9587d","tid":475544,"uid":12416,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"但係選址咁奇怪嘅 隔離就係堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d6be62bc3d269cd96d296149050c9818ea7238","tid":475544,"uid":40763,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"19億咁撚平 抵起<br />\n起條天橋都成億啦屌你老味"},{"pid":"e41929c32b72103c1c24eedaca910ae7de7f9bba","tid":475544,"uid":48,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"對比條膠鐵 好抵起 起多十個唔該"},{"pid":"154d6e2184c28f89868c73c1aa8c9535576b11df","tid":475544,"uid":11840,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19億咁撚平 抵起<br />\n起條天橋都成億啦屌你老味</blockquote><br />\n立法會同中信條橋<br />\n有水舞間睇 值回票價"},{"pid":"055c3d150a3c4368a6a216d4764100192bbd5f1b","tid":475544,"uid":4363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edc1820050be28ca5df2b4c539be1eccb6965d0","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對比條膠鐵 好抵起 起多十個唔該</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠鐵: 1117億<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳建海水化淡廠 (中型廠): 93億 (9%用水量), 要起3年<br />\n<br />\n水塘: 35%用水量<br />\n<br />\n數學題：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 起多少間海水化淡廠, 香港就可以水資源自給自足？<br />\n<br />\n(2) 要多久, 香港就可以水資源自給自足？"},{"pid":"979672bcbf08502fdcb9ea744b4d3941bd6e053e","tid":475544,"uid":6183,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9"},{"pid":"ef40e45e066a2a126bf06d96d2a2316b0cb6f277","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保共黨都唔想飲屎水毒水架<br />\n<br />\n係得五毛咁痴線話要飲屎水毒水要感恩囉"},{"pid":"8177a75d40e5aa8dd06de4b3774411e8bb6bf13d","tid":475544,"uid":6799,"li