ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41d28da1d9afd4ad70514a78a189a21a73ea7c1","tid":475544,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇人反對?? 呢單野真係冇古怪??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲東江水班保皇黨都有份飲㗎嘛,佢哋口講話乾淨啫</blockquote><br />\n水佢地自己都飲喎<br />\n正如撐港教育但送仔女讀國際學校<br />\n<br />\n或者知內情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5501e522304545cf98c4e92151c97e0af0ad4616","tid":475544,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"0反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98be8b75d4056555ab1e1a61e5bb9995294e1eb9","tid":475544,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到"},{"pid":"3c48005917b16cbef8204c86634f1fb2e4cf09fe","tid":475544,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為現實上呢個係民生問題黎，如果冇第二條路，水費大升之日就會對建制派做成好大政治壓力"},{"pid":"2733c1f11667476b085bd9cf12d076ab5370451b","tid":475544,"uid":1654,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為現實上呢個係民生問題黎，如果冇第二條路，水費大升之日就會對建制派做成好大政治壓力</blockquote><br />\n領匯上市，屋邨街市買餸好貴，有壓力咩，死廢老投完票都唔知邊個黎"},{"pid":"8003dee7d7d71564a64c81c263f7787eec8b1a81","tid":475544,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為現實上呢個係民生問題黎，如果冇第二條路，水費大升之日就會對建制派做成好大政治壓力</blockquote><br />\n領匯上市，屋邨街市買餸好貴，有壓力咩，死廢老投完票都唔知邊個黎</blockquote><br />\n你講得啱 主要係海水化淡好似本身就無人(組織)有好大反對意見"},{"pid":"3fc4277050f49b977b8fe4c3fc4df7248295b8e8","tid":475544,"uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"焚化爐仲撚重要喇 之前班仆街又搞事"},{"pid":"bc24086085ad1464d99df86e9eb4e3a516f5548c","tid":475544,"uid":48670,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"堡主內應已經滲透入港共政府<br />\n港獨計劃依照藍圖進行中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2156a39f053f8f368bacbf1aafbea5b82852a80e","tid":475544,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17fadd038498cd78811a9b75584e42f338c9bd1","tid":475544,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"其實最重要原因都係建制派自己都想飲乾淨水，身體夠誠實"},{"pid":"709c88176e261be89b6edd9c63983821cc711503","tid":475544,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9</blockquote><br />\n選舉時有人提出要起海水化淡<br />\n都比建制屌爆笑鳩佢妙想天開<br />\n而家佢地又覺得無問題</blockquote><br />\n今次建制唔反對 好神奇"},{"pid":"ede82df78f50ce8b9b812789de057e43e0d53a57","tid":475544,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">劉國勳對東江水供水協議不能使用新收費模式感失望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n粵港雙方達成新東江水供水協議，未來3年總額水價為144億2100萬元，較上一份協議增加6.9%，收費方式維持不變，繼續是「統包總額」方式。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員劉國勳，對港府不能使用新收費模式感失望，期望下次雙方商討2020年供水協定時，可採用混合方式，以一個固定金額付費以確保一個保證的供水量，高於供水量時則再按額外供水量，繳付浮動金額。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員黃碧雲指，曾於考察東江水時接觸廣東省官員，形容對方寸步不讓，加上本港過度依賴東江水，未有發展本地供水方式，令港府的議價能力大大降低，即使廣東省方面再加價，香港也只能被逼接受。<br />\n<br />\n她建議，本港應研究擴建或再興建新水塘，以及興建海水化淡廠，避免依賴東江水。"},{"pid":"15f94194f773dcc37f2583e44b46d655afee1c7a","tid":475544,"uid":63154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"恐怖想像題：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試想像一場工業意外，上面唔覺意倒瀉咗十幾噸山埃落東江，事情會點發展？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐慌程度不下於大亞灣核電廠爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3472a0054338852ac53921cd5c1da636c3f3aeda","tid":475544,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海水淡化廠之後第二步就係發展輕工業同農業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n現實：政府賣哂d地皮比地產商起樓 又賺一筆天價收入"},{"pid":"b81944a1fea440c0dd49bfbeace97c4411e2a105","tid":475544,"uid":62650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"19億又幾抵wor, 呢個係今年最好既德政"},{"pid":"4518b3f9345d10e14924755ba2303aa6ad5afe09","tid":475544,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07abc4e7f19f5a64d5e6ef99fc97f93ddac2e293","tid":475544,"uid":148332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">將軍澳海水化淡廠 11億元建水管</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據水務署向立法會提交的文件，建議將將軍澳海水化淡廠第一階段設計及建造的一部分提升為甲級工程，<span style=\"color: red;\">以建設一條長約10公里、直徑1,200毫米的食水管</span>，連接化淡廠及配水庫，造價達11.1億港元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.hket.com/article/1625163/將軍澳海水化淡廠%2011億元建水管\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1625163%2F%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%252011%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E5%BB%BA%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=dfc10164\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.hket.com/article/1625163/將軍澳海水化淡廠%2011億元建水管</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯定用強國貨啦,今次又唔知條水管入面有咩元素"},{"pid":"27d99a24335b5fb2c4c41a84ba2af23dd1c35406","tid":475544,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61ae9e84841699478975cd80d05df5ae5601d4fb","tid":475544,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>97前要英國佬走前<br />\n炸咗個海水化淡廠<br />\n現在又起翻<br />\n尋來浪費金錢</blockquote><br />\n你都戇鳩<br />\n你估而家仲係蒸溜化淡咩"},{"pid":"3d55bd02dafa4be277b27d1011d87bc93f7cfa32","tid":475544,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係選址咁奇怪嘅 隔離就係堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔籬係小西灣同東龍洲添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少見多怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經有工業邨隔住可以由深水工業改劃住宅區起樓重用康城噉嘅印象..."},{"pid":"696eb449a6a169a1b931a467b9a2043b5a4d3da6","tid":475544,"uid":148332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"呢幾年唯一聽到既好消息"},{"pid":"99447c6fc7d515d3808c17eb19ff5387596ebde1","tid":475544,"uid":131423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解建制唔會反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對會比人屌爆，建制邊會咁on9</blockquote><br />\n選舉時有人提出要起海水化淡<br />\n都比建制屌爆笑鳩