\n建制派 幾乎全部人都有外國護照, 家人又多數住係外國/留學<br />\n佢地根本唔會關心香港有冇乾淨水"},{"pid":"7a597d631c351fba5e66902619b8992721f292a0","tid":475544,"uid":133375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚西咩 之前有個連登鍵國大師話三個月夠整個供應全香港嘅淡化廠啦</blockquote><br />\n3年東江水費都100幾億<br />\n攞黎起化淡<br />\n供返水上去都夠有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0aba04f42887ed7c7c1a04b96bf99a20d651a2","tid":475544,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但成個香港咁大，19 億既海水化淡會唔會負荷唔到</blockquote><br />\n只夠幾個%用,短期都仲係靠東江水同水塘</blockquote><br />\n點解政府意識唔到大陸當香港係水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔知點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你以為香港政府意識唔到??<br />\n香港政府只係中共政府既傀儡............中共政府叫佢地做乜, 佢地就照做嫁啦"},{"pid":"d65714f525911c71a609f925cee17c434f8e4993","tid":475544,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>起碼香港水務署信得過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你緊係冇聽開雲海節目<br />\n水務署職員親口講d水過濾完都仲係有層乳白色既野 要用大量藥粉倒落岡水度先勉強變返清 果d係咩物質就不得而知 而且果d藥粉咁大量吸入唔知有冇咩事"},{"pid":"aa2a29770a5b269215f9767345aebfca9e3d1d8f","tid":475544,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾港啲海水......"},{"pid":"73bb41f3dc38d48cf86609f0ab253189a368c7d8","tid":475544,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"平撚過買屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c7d35663c08100f347c67245f07d0cca7245f8","tid":475544,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾港啲海水......</blockquote><br />\n垃圾港d海水都易過濾過東江元素水喇"},{"pid":"19116dbd9994